    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is looking for a new home where it can get the serious TLC it deserves. While it's currently in poor condition and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it represents a fantastic opportunity for someone handy to take on a rewarding restoration project. If you're looking for a budget-friendly way to get a car with potential, this is the one for you!",
